Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an6}这\N个\N可\N以\N有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,358)}都说是一个意思了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,358)}你要软到什么程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:23:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,358)}好
